Quickstrike:

"Aw, dang it!" Quickstrike turned around and looked at the vent face. He 
walked up to the wall. He attempted to jump up into the vent, but he was too 
short to reach it. He tried two more times, but with no avail.

"Beast mode." Quickstrike transformed to beast mode and climbed up the wall, 
into the air shaft. He crawled around inside it, and called, "Dark Mouse. 
Dark Mouse? Where are ya rodent?"





Megatron:

"Ah, a good logical bot." he said. He stood up. "I belive it's time for us 
to return their glory. It doesn't make sense for fellow Predacons to fight 
amoung themselves while we can put out energies into fighting the Maximals 
and even the Alliance. A Predacon uses team work. What you need is an 
experienced leader like myself."
